FDSec





  A Windows cyber security tool



I have written this project in C# because it should be easier than other languages.
Malware uses to kill services and processes to avoid monitoring and interruptions, so I have decided to write the code to check services running or stopping.
Windows Defender;
Windows Firewall;
Windows Update;
Security Service Center;
Shadow copies;
Malware uses to delete backups and logs with commandLine.
powershell;
vssadmin.exe;
wbadmin.exe;
diskshadow.exe;
wmic.exe;
wevtutil;
auditpol.exe;
net.exe;
sc.exe;
Monitoring processes will help to detect cancellations.
